creator: Various
description: LibriVox Christmas Short Works Collection 2013. Read in English by BookAngel7, Winston Tharp, Annise, Pam Castille, ravenotation, Ruth Golding, ACBowgus, Martin Reyto, Lucy Perry, Laurie Anne Walden, Carol Box, Greg Giordano, MaryAnn, David Wales. Read in German by Elli and in Finnish by Mari Mattila. A selection of poems, short stories and other prose for the Christmas season in English, Finnish and German. This collection includes stories and prose by Dickens, Thackeray, Arnold Bennett, O. Henry, R. L. Stevenson, Henry van Dyke, Mary Roberts Rinehart, Frank R. Stockton, Susan Coolidge and Christopher Morley, poetry by Sidney Lanier and Paul Laurence Dunbar, pieces in German by Hans Christian Andersen and Rainer Maria Rilke, and a Finnish poem by Zacharias Topelius. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the https://librivox.org/christmas-short-works-collection-2013/ for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
